    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into a separate bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Combine your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and<strong> chopped coconut flakes </strong>in another bowl – these are your <strong>coconut breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
