        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the<strong> jumbo prawns </strong>in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add into the <strong>beaten egg </strong>and finally press into the <strong>coconut breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over – these are your <strong>breaded jumbo prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
